        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer514277494" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8349503077887379987">Worthy epic of a nation and people many many centuries old. Full of iranian mythology, wars (a lot of it), romances, heroes, villains and shahs. Ferdowsi deserves the honor and praise he receives. Composed a century or so after the arab conquest, it helps preserve the stories and legends of pre-islamic Persia for future generations. If you enjoy other epics, you&apos;ll the Shahnameh.</span>
  <span id="freeText8349503077887379987" style="display:none">Worthy epic of a nation and people many many centuries old. Full of iranian mythology, wars (a lot of it), romances, heroes, villains and shahs. Ferdowsi deserves the honor and praise he receives. Composed a century or so after the arab conquest, it helps preserve the stories and legends of pre-islamic Persia for future generations. If you enjoy other epics, you'll the Shahnameh.</span>
