<div id="review_1110641594" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1110641594" />
    <a title="Yasaman" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/34493714-yasaman"><img alt="Yasaman" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1478554590p2/34493714.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1110641594?book_show_action=true">Nov 19, 2014</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Yasaman" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Yasaman" href="/user/show/34493714-yasaman">Yasaman</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/34493714-yasaman?shelf=persian-golden-age">persian-golden-age</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/34493714-yasaman?shelf=poetry-mythology">poetry-mythology</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1110641594" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18285803239655354009">Reading this epic&apos;s stories and knowing them by heart is part of being an Iranian. It&apos;s one of the richest and one of the most important sources of Persian literature, language, culture, mythology, and history. Ferdowsi&apos;s work is a national treasure and, although in his time it wasn&apos;t regarded as such, it certainly is today.</span>
  <span id="freeText18285803239655354009" style="display:none">Reading this epic's stories and knowing them by heart is part of being an Iranian. It's one of the richest and one of the most important sources of Persian literature, language, culture, mythology, and history. Ferdowsi's work is a national treasure and, although in his time it wasn't regarded as such, it certainly is today.</span>
